{"tid":1653592,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【說好的制裁？】停播不足一周　騰訊復播NBA季前賽","createTime":"2019-10-14T06:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T09:58:47.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"608504252f1f0b5efe5c7aff868062e707382465","tid":1653592,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3403899/org/0ee5f9b77f9fa151b279d7e10b1cc931.jpg/6ifajI671GdVWo5bhePwUooexyb06zDD90tqD_dLag8?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3403899%2Forg%2F0ee5f9b77f9fa151b279d7e10b1cc931.jpg%2F6ifajI671GdVWo5bhePwUooexyb06zDD90tqD_dLag8%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=2e7b5380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經歷不足一星期的停播風波後，騰訊體育周一（14日）早上已開始恢復播放NBA季前賽。<br />\n<br />\n不過風波的「始作俑者」火箭，所出戰的賽事則仍然未在直播節目表之中。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊體育官方網站上今天NBA的直播節目表顯示，已恢復部分比賽直播，分別有北京時間早上6時公牛對速龍，以及8時以色列馬卡比對木狼。周二（15日）6場季前賽則顯示會有「圖文直播」。在騰訊視頻的平台上，以色列馬卡比對木狼的點播次數為2818，而精華片段則有1.4萬的瀏覽量。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於NBA火箭隊總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）早前挺港言論在內地引發軒然大波，直播節目表上，火箭在北京時間周四主場對馬刺的比賽仍然沒有安排直播。<br />\n<br />\nNBA賽事在騰訊平台上的地位舉足輕重，早前剛以5年15億美元取得NBA在內地的網路轉播權。根據統計，在2018/19賽季中，通過騰訊平台觀看NBA賽事直播和網路節目達到4.9億人次，當季總決賽第六場比賽的直播超過2100萬球迷觀看，上述數字均創下內地網絡平台的單場NBA賽事收視人數之最。<br />\n<br />\n不過，騰訊體育8日才在官方微博宣布，即日起暫停NBA季前賽中國賽的轉播安排；同時為2019年9月7日之後才購入火箭直播通行證、但還未更改球隊選擇的用戶退款。在此之前，中央廣播電視台央視體育頻道亦發表聲明 ，決定立即暫停NBA賽事轉播安排。<br />\n<br />\n如今恢復轉播NBA賽事，引起不少網友攻擊，網民在內地論壇紛紛留言，表示：「暫停了兩三天就完事了？？」、「沒個NBA還不活了？ 」。不過亦有人表示，「既然能直播了證明國家允許了，國家都允許了你還這秀愛國」、「那人家看NBA犯法了嗎？都不犯法你們一天到晚巡邏個什麼勁呢」等，表示支持復播的決定。"},{"pid":"cdea3bfa45c7bc2639a5f2e9a3ea364048de3d45","tid":1653592,"uid":213893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"聽國家號召毁咗約停止合作嗰班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n挽撚猿"},{"pid":"e6425d47f791d6bf25e535693869776d06853b8c","tid":1653592,"uid":215947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"痴返個玻璃心"},{"pid":"36d3fc0291d0e6a3044a86db4944f6c80a834cce","tid":1653592,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"賤骨頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8516dd35b4cb9051bde6a30bd5cd388fa8b550ac","tid":1653592,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"所以啤梨真係屌得好啱，支那人係最撚下賤、最撚仆街民族！"},{"pid":"742a3795441d4876c4f864a5e3f5ebb352123bed","tid":1653592,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdea3bfa45c7bc2639a5f2e9a3ea364048de3d45","tid":1653592,"uid":213893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"聽國家號召毁咗約停止合作嗰班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n挽撚猿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"放心啦,中央一定會堅定支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a12252302f019a04be9fcc8255848c66da57c1","tid":1653592,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8516dd35b4cb9051bde6a30bd5cd388fa8b550ac","tid":1653592,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"所以啤梨真係屌得好啱，支那人係最撚下賤、最撚仆街民族！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1614de61035aa0e6253b6c1841c4d3